Last but not the least my dear constant supporters @_mansaaaaaaaa_ @kratika_kansal14 @pallllavi_ @namita221299 @aayushijain_hair @shubhamaparajita without you guys this phase of Amisha wouldn’t be there🫶🏻🫶🏻🫶🏻

latestPosts.caption:
Balancing both✅️
Embracing both✨️
.
.
I've lately realized a good balance between work & workout is so much required, none of them should be more than 50%. 
I tried once giving extra priority to each at a time but failed to chase either of them. Growth stopped, moreover mental peace hampered alot. 
Lesson learned though🤓
.
.
.
